Class AsynchronousStackSinkAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • clearcontrol.stack.sourcesink.sink.AsynchronousStackSinkAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    StackSinkInterface, StackSinkSourceInterface

    public class AsynchronousStackSinkAdapter
extends java.lang.Object
implements StackSinkInterface
    Asynchronous stack sink adapter. This sink adapter can wrap anotehr sink an provides asynchronous decoupling via an elastic queue.

    royer
